# 🚀 Production Deployment Plan - Separate React App

**Goal:** Deploy image similarity search system to company server as a standalone React application

**Current State:** Development environment (localhost)  
**Target State:** Production-ready separate React app + Backend API

---

## 📋 Overview

**Deployment Architecture:**

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│    Company Server (Production)              │
│                                              │
│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐   │
│  │   Nginx (Port 80/443)               │   │
│  │   - Serves React static files       │   │
│  │   - Reverse proxy for /api          │   │
│  └─────────────┬───────────────────────┘   │
│                │                             │
│  ┌─────────────▼───────────────────────┐   │
│  │   FastAPI Backend (Port 8000)       │   │
│  │   - Search API                      │   │
│  │   - Docker containers               │   │
│  └─────────────┬───────────────────────┘   │
│                │                             │
│  ┌─────────────▼───────────────────────┐   │
│  │   PostgreSQL + Redis + MinIO        │   │
│  │   - Docker containers               │   │
│  └─────────────────────────────────────┘   │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

---

## 🎯 Action Plan

### Phase 1: Pre-Deployment Preparation (2-3 hours)

#### 1.1 Update Production Configuration

**Create production environment file:**

```bash
# Create .env.production (DO NOT COMMIT TO GIT)
cp .env .env.production
```

**Edit `.env.production`:**

```properties
# Database
POSTGRES_HOST=127.0.0.1
POSTGRES_PORT=5434
POSTGRES_USER=admin
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=<GENERATE_STRONG_PASSWORD>  # Use: openssl rand -base64 32
POSTGRES_DB=vectordb

# Redis
REDIS_URL=redis://127.0.0.1:6379/0

# MinIO/S3 (Production)
MINIO_ENDPOINT=https://s3.yourcompany.com  # Update with actual endpoint
MINIO_ROOT_USER=<PRODUCTION_ACCESS_KEY>
MINIO_ROOT_PASSWORD=<PRODUCTION_SECRET_KEY>
MINIO_BUCKET_NAME=image-similarity-prod
MINIO_USE_SSL=true

# Security
WEBHOOK_SECRET=<GENERATE_SECRET>  # Use: openssl rand -hex 32
API_KEY=<GENERATE_API_KEY>  # Use: openssl rand -base64 32

# Application
INGEST_QUEUE_BACKEND=rq
INGEST_QUEUE_NAME=minio_ingestion
INGEST_JOB_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=900
```

**Action Items:**
