### Phase 2: Backend Production Setup (1-2 hours)

#### 2.1 Update CORS for Production Domain

**Edit [app.py](file:///c:/Users/ACHAL.TRIVEDI/Downloads/InHouse-Indexed%20Search/app.py):**

```python
# app.py
from fastapi.middleware.cors import CORSMiddleware

# Production CORS
ALLOWED_ORIGINS = os.getenv("ALLOWED_ORIGINS", "*").split(",")

app.add_middleware(
    CORSMiddleware,
    allow_origins=ALLOWED_ORIGINS,  # In production: ["https://similarity.yourcompany.com"]
    allow_credentials=True,
    allow_methods=["*"],
    allow_headers=["*"],
)
```

**Add to `.env.production`:**
```properties
ALLOWED_ORIGINS=https://similarity.yourcompany.com,https://yourcompany.com
```

---

#### 2.2 Add API Key Authentication (Optional but Recommended)

**Add middleware to [app.py](file:///c:/Users/ACHAL.TRIVEDI/Downloads/InHouse-Indexed%20Search/app.py):**

```python
# app.py
from fastapi import Header, HTTPException

API_KEY = os.getenv("API_KEY")

async def verify_api_key(x_api_key: str = Header(None)):
    if API_KEY and x_api_key != API_KEY:
        raise HTTPException(status_code=403, detail="Invalid API Key")

# Apply to search endpoint
@app.post("/search", dependencies=[Depends(verify_api_key)])
async def search_image(...):
    ...
```

**Action Items:**
- [ ] Update CORS settings
- [ ] Add API key authentication (optional)
- [ ] Test with production domain

