#### 3.3 Configure Nginx

**Create Nginx configuration:**

```bash
sudo nano /etc/nginx/sites-available/image-similarity
```

**Add configuration:**

```nginx
# /etc/nginx/sites-available/image-similarity

# Redirect HTTP to HTTPS
server {
    listen 80;
    server_name similarity.yourcompany.com;
    return 301 https://$server_name$request_uri;
}

# HTTPS server
server {
    listen 443 ssl http2;
    server_name similarity.yourcompany.com;

    # SSL certificates (will be created by Certbot)
    ssl_certificate /etc/letsencrypt/live/similarity.yourcompany.com/fullchain.pem;
    ssl_certificate_key /etc/letsencrypt/live/similarity.yourcompany.com/privkey.pem;
    
    # SSL configuration
    ssl_protocols TLSv1.2 TLSv1.3;
    ssl_ciphers HIGH:!aNULL:!MD5;
    ssl_prefer_server_ciphers on;

    # Root directory for React app
    root /opt/image-similarity/frontend/dist;
    index index.html;

    # Serve static files (React app)
    location / {
        try_files $uri $uri/ /index.html;
        add_header Cache-Control "public, max-age=31536000";  # 1 year cache
    }

    # Proxy API requests to FastAPI backend
    location /api {
        proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:8000;
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;
        
        # Timeouts for large file uploads
        proxy_read_timeout 300;
        proxy_connect_timeout 300;
        proxy_send_timeout 300;
        
        # Increase upload size limit
        client_max_body_size 100M;
    }

    # Health check endpoint
    location /health {
        proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:8000/health;
        access_log off;
    }
}
```

**Enable site:**

```bash
sudo ln -s /etc/nginx/sites-available/image-similarity /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/
sudo nginx -t  # Test configuration
sudo systemctl reload nginx
```

**Action Items:**
- [ ] Create Nginx configuration
- [ ] Enable site
- [ ] Test Nginx config

