### Phase 5: Production Hardening (2-3 hours)

#### 5.1 Setup Database Backups

```bash
# Create backup script
sudo nano /etc/cron.daily/postgres-backup.sh
```

**Add script:**

```bash
#!/bin/bash
BACKUP_DIR="/opt/backups/postgres"
DATE=$(date +%Y%m%d_%H%M%S)

mkdir -p $BACKUP_DIR

docker exec vector_db_prod pg_dump -U admin vectordb | gzip > "$BACKUP_DIR/vectordb_$DATE.sql.gz"

# Keep last 7 days
find $BACKUP_DIR -name "vectordb_*.sql.gz" -mtime +7 -delete

echo "Backup completed: vectordb_$DATE.sql.gz"
```

```bash
sudo chmod +x /etc/cron.daily/postgres-backup.sh

# Test backup
sudo /etc/cron.daily/postgres-backup.sh
```

