#### 5.3 Setup Logging

**Configure log rotation:**

```bash
sudo nano /etc/logrotate.d/image-similarity
```

```
/var/log/nginx/similarity*.log {
    daily
    missingok
    rotate 14
    compress
    delaycompress
    notifempty
    create 0640 www-data adm
    sharedscripts
    postrotate
        systemctl reload nginx > /dev/null
    endscript
}
```

