## 🆘 Troubleshooting

### React App Not Loading
```bash
# Check Nginx logs
sudo tail -f /var/log/nginx/error.log

# Verify dist folder exists
ls -la /opt/image-similarity/frontend/dist

# Rebuild if needed
cd /opt/image-similarity/frontend
npm run build
```

### API Not Responding
```bash
# Check backend logs
docker-compose -f docker-compose.prod.yml logs app

# Check if backend is running
docker ps

# Restart if needed
docker-compose -f docker-compose.prod.yml restart app
```

### Database Connection Issues
```bash
# Check database is running
docker ps | grep vector_db

# Check database logs
docker logs vector_db_prod

# Test connection
docker exec vector_db_prod psql -U admin -d vectordb -c "SELECT 1"
```

